Argued June 21, STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. LARRY ALLEN STRAIN, Appellant. (No. 39491) 510 P2d 1349 Gary D. Babcock, Public Defender, Salem, argued the cause and filed the brief for appellant. Boyle L. Bchiffman, District Attorney, Roseburg, argued the cause for respondent. With him on the brief was Brian R. Barnes, Deputy District Attorney, Roseburg.

affirmed June 21, 1973

Before Schwab, Chief Judge, and Foley and Thornton, Judges.
